{
  "stem": "26728.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "These guys came down the stairs and-- and they-- they shot them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't  know 20, 15, 20.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't really know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I didn't even think anything about that because I thought they had been in a firefight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But this was a whole different situation here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was where they were shooting down unarmed men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And like I say, in retrospect, I probably would have participated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't think I could do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Gut wise, I don't think I have the guts to do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I was enraged to the point where I didn't feel bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when you-- you know, the thing that about that whole incident that bothered me the most was not the fact that they-- that they-- and thinking in retrospect, even today, was the-- the one man going over with a 45 and blowing another guy's head off.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, that you could see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, you could see him pick out the guy, because he was still moving, and put the gun and pull the trigger.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And you could see the guy's head pop like a watermelon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that-- that got me worse than watching them shoot them down in bunches, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And OK, so that-- that-- tht incident was-- was-- that was pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Later, I think-- I think I left the camp before sundown.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And here again we had-- had taken over-- they had taken over some houses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the in-- the infantry division-- there were two infantry divisions involved-- continued on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They left some guards behind, 400 or 500 guards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- but they continued on with their troops or tank support and what, to take Munich.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
